  - account-invite.get.ts, account-invite.post.ts, account-invite/[id].delete.ts, account-invite/accept.post.ts, account-invite/validate.get.ts
  - account-register.post.ts, account-register.delete.ts, account-register-sort.post.ts
  - account-registers/forecast-balances.get.ts
- Budgets and categories
  - budget.post.ts, budget/[id].patch.ts, budget/[id].delete.ts, budget/[id]/reset.post.ts
  - categories.get.ts, category.post.ts, category.patch.ts, category.delete.ts
- Registers and entries
  - register.ts
  - register-entry.post.ts, register-entry.patch.ts, register-entry.delete.ts
  - register-entry-transfer.post.ts, register-entry-transfer-create.post.ts
  - register-entry-applied.post.ts, register-entry-skip.post.ts, register-entry-match-reoccurrence.post.ts
  - snapshot.post.ts, snapshots.get.ts, snapshot/[id].get.ts, snapshot/[id].delete.ts, snapshot-register/[id].get.ts
- Reoccurrences and health
  - reoccurrence.post.ts, reoccurrence.delete.ts, reoccurrence-health.get.ts
- Reports
