- Bills
  - bills.get.ts, bills/profile/[id].patch.ts, bill-instance/[id].patch.ts, bills/reminders/evaluate.post.ts
- Reconciliation
  - reconciliation/period.get.ts, period.post.ts, periods/open.get.ts
  - reconciliation/period/[id].get.ts, period/[id]/close.post.ts, item/[entryId].patch.ts
